{"about_the_game":"When Master left the atelier, Riblo, an alchemist, suddenly began to stand alone.<br><br>Riblo explores new places Meet various people, She comes across multiple experiences.<br>To Riblo, who has never been outside the Pipi Forest, The outside world is full of new and mysterious things.<br>Will Riblo be able to safely make &quot;Philosopher's Stone&quot; and solve Master's homework?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/image_alchemy_en.gif?t=1731941838\" /><br>\u3010Alchemy using the Alchemy Pot\u3011<br>Riblo is an alchemist who can collect various ingredients and combine items<br>in the alchemy pot.<br>The combined item can be used for the residents who need help by progressing the episode<br>or receiving a quest.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/image_material_en.png?t=1731941838\" /><br>\u3010Collect various materials\u3011<br>Riblo explores various locations and collects new materials.<br>She may sometimes need alchemy-made items to get the ingredients she wants.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/image_quest_en.png?t=1731941838\" /><br>\u3010Resolving requests from residents\u3011<br>Riblo can solve quests with items made with alchemy.<br>Check out the Quest notes of residents in need on the town board of Pipi Town!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/image_recipe_en.png?t=1731941838\" /><br>\u3010Collect Alchemy Recipe\u3011<br>Riblo can complete the recipe book by registering alchemy recipes.<br>Recipes can be purchased at the Pipi Town Recipe Store.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/image_npc_en.png?t=1731941838\" /><br>\u3010Various ep